{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Monday night, with the help of the Polish underground, where they an inroad into the camp at about 10:10 on a-- on a Monday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You want to-- yeah, yeah, Monday evening, with his help, I escaped.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went through to-- to a guard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was just a guard with-- with one rifle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and he knew the Polish, you see, that they had a permit to come and going in, in and out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we were going, wherever God set his heart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or-- and as well, mister, you weren't in the know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And who is this man?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, well, I-- I forget to tell you that I-- I had an order to take this-- to take this for a friend, out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he told me, don't-- don't-- don't dare to speak Hungarian, or-- or-- or any-- any other language.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not even-- not even in English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't say-- don't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he-- he was just-- and then he did this and that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- and just, he winked at me, and I knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he, when he came in, he brought a loaded pistol.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I already had it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had my hat on-- my hand on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when he winked, I just pulled out and right in the small-- small head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and he just collapsed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we just walked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not far-- not far, there-- there was a German streetcar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Boarded the streetcar in about five minutes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And into the-- into the chapel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was still, on the Buda side, in a [NON-ENGLISH] chapel there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there they were waiting for me already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Behind the altar, there were six-- six or seven people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So this Polish lead me in-- in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a group of resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
